---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="DogGuideHub privacy policy — how we collect, use, and protect your information."
>
  <section class="section legal-page">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: June 2026</p>

      <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
      <p>
        DogGuideHub ("we," "our," or "us") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we
        collect, use, and protect information when you visit dogguidehub.com (the "Site").
      </p>

      <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Email addresses</strong> you voluntarily submit through our newsletter signup form.</li>
        <li><strong>Usage data</strong> such as pages visited, time spent, and referral source, collected automatically through analytics tools.</li>
        <li><strong>Cookies</strong> used for site functionality and analytics purposes.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>To send you newsletters, tips, and updates you've opted in to receive.</li>
        <li>To improve our content and website experience.</li>
        <li>To analyze site traffic and user behavior.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>
        We use third-party services to operate this Site, including Supabase (data storage) and
        MailerLite (email delivery). These providers have their own privacy policies governing the use
        of your information.
      </p>

      <h2>5. Affiliate Links</h2>
      <p>
        This Site contains affiliate links. We may earn a commission when you click on or make a
        purchase through these links, at no additional cost to you. See our
        <a href="/affiliate-disclosure">Affiliate Disclosure</a> for more details.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Your Choices</h2>
      <p>
        You may unsubscribe from our email list at any time using the link provided in every email.
        You may also disable cookies through your browser settings.
      </p>

      <h2>7. Data Security</h2>
      <p>
        We take reasonable measures to protect your information but cannot guarantee absolute security
        of data transmitted over the internet.
      </p>

      <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        This Site is not directed at children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect information
        from children.
      </p>

      <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with
        an updated revision date.
      </p>

      <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at
        <a href="mailto:contact@dogguidehub.com">contact@dogguidehub.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 48px 20px;
  }
  .legal-page h1 { color: var(--primary-dark); }
  .legal-page h2 { margin-top: 32px; color: var(--primary-dark); font-size: 20px; }
  .legal-page p, .legal-page li { color: var(--text-muted); }
  .legal-page ul { padding-left: 22px; }
  .legal-page a { color: var(--primary); font-weight: 600; }
  .updated { font-size: 13px; color: #9ca3af; }
</style>